OL,4,Chigh on cocaine has sentence increased
OL,6,FA driver who killed a 13-year-old boy
OL,7,Fwhile high on cocaine and alcohol has
OL,8,Fhad his sentence increased at the
OL,9,FCourt of Appeal.
OL,11,FHarley Whiteman drove into Kaylan
OL,12,FHippsley as he and his friends walked
OL,13,Fto a community centre in Hirwaun,
OL,14,FRhondda Cynon, in February this year.
OL,16,FWhiteman, who pleaded guilty to death
OL,17,Fby dangerous driving, had been given a
OL,18,Fsentence of six years and nine months
OL,19,Fat Merthyr Tydfil Crown Court in April.
