OL,3,CDriver who killed 13-year-old while
OL,4,Chigh on cocaine has sentence increased
OL,6,FHowever, on Wednesday, judges in
OL,7,FLondon extended this to nine years,
OL,8,Ffollowing a referral by the Solicitor
OL,9,FGeneral.
OL,11,FA driving ban was also extended to 11
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FSome members of Kaylan's family and
OL,15,Ffriends who attended the hearing could
OL,16,Fbe seen crying as the new sentence was
OL,17,Fimposed.
