OL,3,CDriver who killed 13-year-old while
OL,4,Chigh on cocaine has sentence increased
OL,6,FThey had spoken to ITV Wales in May
OL,7,Fabout their determination to make sure
OL,8,Fno other family has to go through what
OL,9,Fthey did.
OL,11,FKelly Brocklehurst, representing the
OL,12,Fsolicitor general, told the court
OL,13,FKaylan's death was "very tragic and
OL,14,Funavoidable", and that the original
OL,15,Fsentence was "unduly lenient".
OL,17,FThe court heard that Whiteman, who was
OL,18,F19 at the time of the incident, drank
OL,19,Ffour pints and had a line of cocaine
OL,20,Fat two pubs in the Welsh village
OL,21,Fearlier this year.
