OL,6,FWhiteman then drove off before
OL,7,Freturning on foot a short while later.
OL,9,FThe court heard that Whiteman began
OL,10,F"holding Kaylan's hand" as the victim
OL,11,Fwas tended to on the floor before
OL,12,Fmembers of the public asked him to
OL,13,Fleave, believing him to be under the
OL,14,Finfluence of alcohol and drugs.
OL,16,FAfter being asked to leave, Whiteman
OL,17,Fsaid: "Do you think I give a f***
OL,18,Fabout this kid on the floor?"
