OL,6,FJames Hartson, representing Whiteman,
OL,7,Ftold the court the now 20-year-old was
OL,8,F"still a very young man" with "a
OL,9,Fplethora of mitigation".
OL,11,FHe made a "dreadful set of choices",
OL,12,FMr Hartson added and said Whiteman had
OL,13,Fan "extremely immature" attitude.
OL,15,FAfter his arrest, Whiteman told
OL,16,Fofficers he was "aware of a little
OL,17,Fbang" when he struck Kaylan "but
OL,18,Fthought he had just hit the curb", the
OL,19,Fcourt heard.
