OL,6,FThe court was told in a victim impact
OL,7,Fstatement that Kaylan's grandmother `
OL,8,Fwhom the teenager had lived with ` "no
OL,9,Flonger had a purpose in life".
OL,11,FHis sister said in a second victim
OL,12,Fimpact statement that "she could not
OL,13,Fbear to be anywhere that reminded her
OL,14,Fof him".
OL,16,FIncreasing the sentence, Lord Justice
OL,17,FWilliam Davis, sitting alongside Mrs
OL,18,FJustice Thornton and Judge Michael
OL,19,FChambers KC, said Whiteman had been
OL,20,Fpreviously described as "abhorrent and
OL,21,Fheartless ... and totally unrepentant".
