OL,6,FHe added: "There is nothing this court
OL,7,Fcan do to assist the grief the family
OL,8,Fhas for Kaylan."
OL,10,FAfter the hearing, solicitor general
OL,11,FSarah Sackman MP said: "Harley
OL,12,FWhiteman's reckless actions have
OL,13,Fbroken a family and stolen the life of
OL,14,Fa 13-year-old boy.
OL,16,F"That Whiteman fled the scene before
OL,17,Fabusing people tending to Kaylan, as
OL,18,Fwell as police officers, is utterly
OL,19,Fdeplorable.
